'''天主教邦杜庫教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Bondukuensis}}；{{lang-fr|Diocèse de Bondoukou}}）是[[科特迪瓦|科特迪瓦]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教布瓦凱總教區|布瓦凱總教區]]。

教區成立於1987年7月3日，<ref>{{cite web |title=BONDUKUENSIS* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19870703_bondukuensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822180606/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19870703_bondukuensis.html |archivedate=2019-08-22 |language=la |date=1987-07-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>包括[[桑桑區|桑桑區]]。2006年有教友97,800人（佔轄區總人口14.4%）、十六個堂區、四十三名司鐸。現任教區主教為{{link-de|勃路諾·厄索·耶多|Bruno Essoh Yedoh}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 28.06.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/06/28/190628e.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822172212/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/06/28/190628e.html |archivedate=2019-08-22 |language=en |date=2019-06-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

